title: Hannah Montana: The Movie Soundtrack
description:
Hannah Montana: The Movie is the soundtrack to the film of the same name, set to be released on March 24, 2009 on Walt Disney Records. On the soundtrack, songs are performed by Miley Cyrus, both as Cyrus and Hannah Montana, Billy Ray Cyrus, Rascal Flatts, and Taylor Swift.
